<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rachud" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4516971); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4516971&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610160419" alt="Rachud" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4516971)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rachud" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4516971); return false;">Rachud</a></span></p>
